hw9: 

based off of ex19 and ex18

Makes instances of the letter F that rain down from the sky.
There is a single wally hidden in the oddlaw textures, you can change which F has it with r.

Key bindings
  t			 Pause/unpause time
  r			 Change the random wally
  arrows     Change view angle
  PgDn/PgUp  Zoom in and out
  0          Reset view angle
  ESC        Exit

  I spent about 12 hours on this